<Layout title="Cybersecurity Kits for Small Teams – SMBCyberHub" description="Download cybersecurity kits, policies, and audit-ready training. No logins, no subscriptions, GDPR-compliant.">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schemaData)}></script>

  <!-- 🏠 Homepage Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-blue-50 py-20 px-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 leading-tight mb-4">
      Cybersecurity Kits for Small Teams
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-8">
      One-time download. No logins. No subscriptions. Just download and protect your business—<strong>audit-ready in 30 minutes</strong>.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 mb-2">
      <a href="/free-sample" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow">
        📥 Get Free Sample Kit
      </a>
      <a href="/kits" class="border border-emerald-600 text-emerald-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-50 transition">
        🧰 Compare Kits
      </a>
      <a href="https://smbcyberhub.gumroad.com/l/prokit" class="bg-emerald-100 border border-emerald-600 text-emerald-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-emerald-200 transition">
        ✅ Get the Complete Kit
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Trusted by 100+ small teams. Downloaded in 20+ countries. Zero logins, zero tracking—compliance made simple.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- 🛠️ How It Works Section (SEO & User Clarity) -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6 text-center">How SMBCyberHub Kits Work</h2>
    <ol class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 text-base list-decimal pl-6">
      <li><strong>Choose Your Kit:</strong> Pick from our Basic or Pro Kit — both are audit-ready and include everything you need.</li>
      <li><strong>Instant Download:</strong> Kits are delivered as a ZIP file, ready to use — no logins, no SaaS, no tracking.</li>
      <li><strong>Customize for Your Team:</strong> Edit policies, checklists, and training materials as needed (Word & PDF).</li>
      <li><strong>Run a Team Session:</strong> Use the included training slides and quizzes to build cyber awareness in 30 minutes or less.</li>
      <li><strong>Be Audit & Insurance Ready:</strong> Keep your signed policies and logs to show insurers or clients — you’re covered!</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600">
      <strong>Who is it for?</strong> Small businesses (1–20 staff), office managers, founders, consultants, and anyone who needs rapid, real-world cybersecurity compliance.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ✅ Why Choose SMBCyberHub -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-left">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-6 text-center">Why Choose SMBCyberHub?</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-sm">
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">✅ Audit-Ready in 30 Minutes</span><br />
        Prebuilt policies, training, checklists — ready to print or PDF for insurers or clients.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">✅ No Logins, No Subscriptions</span><br />
        One-time download. Offline-ready. Yours forever — not SaaS.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">✅ GDPR & ISO27001 Aligned</span><br />
        Built by a 20+ year IT/compliance veteran. Covers what auditors expect.
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="font-semibold">✅ Built for Non-Tech Teams</span><br />
        Office managers and business owners — no IT background needed.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 text-sm">
      <strong>Learn more:</strong> <a href="/about/" class="text-blue-800 underline">About Us</a> • <a href="/faq/" class="text-blue-800 underline">FAQ</a> • <a href="/blog/" class="text-blue-800 underline">Insights Blog</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- ❓ Quick FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-10 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 text-base">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Do I need IT experience to use these kits?</h3>
        <p>No — all materials are designed for non-technical users. If you can onboard a new hire, you can run this training.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Is it a subscription?</h3>
        <p>No. All kits are a one-time download. No subscriptions, logins, or SaaS.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold">Can I see a sample?</h3>
